hh3cIKEMonitor.name: hh3cIKEMonitor
hh3cIKEMonitor.contactinfo: Platform Team Hangzhou H3C Tech. Co., Ltd. Hai-Dian District Beijing P.R. China http://www.h3c.com Zip:100085
hh3cIKEMonitor.description: The MIB is designed to get statistic information of IKE tunnels. With this MIB, we can get information of a certain IKE tunnel or all IKE tunnels

Hh3cIKEAuthMethod.name: Hh3cIKEAuthMethod
Hh3cIKEAuthMethod.description: The authentication method used in IKE negotiations.

Hh3cDiffHellmanGrp.name: Hh3cDiffHellmanGrp
Hh3cDiffHellmanGrp.description: The Diffie Hellman Group used in IKE and IPSec negotiations.

Hh3cEncryptAlgo.name: Hh3cEncryptAlgo
Hh3cEncryptAlgo.description: The encryption algorithm used in IKE and IPSec negotiations.

Hh3cAuthAlgo.name: Hh3cAuthAlgo
Hh3cAuthAlgo.description: The authentication algorithm used in IKE negotiations.

Hh3cTrapStatus.name: Hh3cTrapStatus
Hh3cTrapStatus.description: The switch which determines whether send a trap or not.

Hh3cTrafficType.name: Hh3cTrafficType
Hh3cTrafficType.description: The type of the data flow.

Hh3cIKETunnelState.name: Hh3cIKETunnelState
Hh3cIKETunnelState.description: The state of the IKE tunnel.

hh3cIKETunnelTable.name: hh3cIKETunnelTable
hh3cIKETunnelTable.description: The IPSec Phase-1 Internet Key Exchange Tunnel Table. There is one entry in this table for each active IPSec Phase-1 IKE Tunnel.

hh3cIKETunnelEntry.name: hh3cIKETunnelEntry
hh3cIKETunnelEntry.description: The entry contains the information about hh3cIKETunnelTable, such as negotiate mode, encryption algorithm and authentication algorithm, etc.

hh3cIKETunIndex.name: hh3cIKETunIndex
hh3cIKETunIndex.description: The index of the IPSec Phase-1 IKE Tunnel Table. The value of the index is a number which begins at one and is incremented with each tunnel that is created. The value of this object will wrap at 2,147,483,647.

hh3cIKETunLocalType.name: hh3cIKETunLocalType
hh3cIKETunLocalType.description: The type of local peer identity.

hh3cIKETunLocalValue1.name: hh3cIKETunLocalValue1
hh3cIKETunLocalValue1.description: The value of the local peer identity. If the local peer type is an IP Address, then this is the IP Address used to identify the local peer. If the local peer type is a host name, then this is the host name used to identify the local peer. If the local peer type is IP subnet, then this is the value of the subnet. If the local peer type is IP address range, then this is the value of beginning IP address of the range.

hh3cIKETunLocalValue2.name: hh3cIKETunLocalValue2
hh3cIKETunLocalValue2.description: The second specification of local peer's IP address. If the local peer type is single IP address or single name, then this is zero-length. If the local peer type is IP subnet, then this is the value of the subnet mask. If the local peer type is IP address range, then this is the value of ending IP address of the range.

hh3cIKETunLocalAddr.name: hh3cIKETunLocalAddr
hh3cIKETunLocalAddr.description: The IP address of the local endpoint for the IPSec Phase-1 IKE Tunnel.

hh3cIKETunRemoteType.name: hh3cIKETunRemoteType
hh3cIKETunRemoteType.description: The type of remote peer identity. The remote peer may be identified by: 1. an IP address, or 2. a host name.

hh3cIKETunRemoteValue1.name: hh3cIKETunRemoteValue1
hh3cIKETunRemoteValue1.description: The value of the remote peer identity. If the remote peer type is an IP Address, then this is the IP Address used to identify the remote peer. If the remote peer type is a host name, then this is the host name used to identify the remote peer. If the remote peer type is IP subnet, then this is the value of the subnet. If the remote peer type is IP address range, then this is the value of beginning IP address of the range.

hh3cIKETunRemoteValue2.name: hh3cIKETunRemoteValue2
hh3cIKETunRemoteValue2.description: The second specification of remote peer's IP address. If the remote peer type is single IP address or single name, then this is zero-length. If the remote peer type is IP subnet, then this is the value of the subnet mask. If the remote peer type is IP address range, then this is the value of ending IP address of the range.

hh3cIKETunRemoteAddr.name: hh3cIKETunRemoteAddr
hh3cIKETunRemoteAddr.description: The IP address of the remote peer for the IPSec Phase-1 IKE Tunnel.

hh3cIKETunNegoMode.name: hh3cIKETunNegoMode
hh3cIKETunNegoMode.description: The negotiation mode of the IPSec Phase-1 IKE Tunnel.

hh3cIKETunDiffHellmanGrp.name: hh3cIKETunDiffHellmanGrp
hh3cIKETunDiffHellmanGrp.description: The Diffie Hellman Group used in the IPSec Phase-1 IKE negotiations.

hh3cIKETunEncryptAlgo.name: hh3cIKETunEncryptAlgo
hh3cIKETunEncryptAlgo.description: The encryption algorithm used in the IPSec Phase-1 IKE negotiations.

hh3cIKETunHashAlgo.name: hh3cIKETunHashAlgo
hh3cIKETunHashAlgo.description: The hash algorithm used in the IPSec Phase-1 IKE negotiations.

hh3cIKETunAuthMethod.name: hh3cIKETunAuthMethod
hh3cIKETunAuthMethod.description: The authentication method used in the IPSec Phase-1 IKE negotiations.

hh3cIKETunLifeTime.name: hh3cIKETunLifeTime
hh3cIKETunLifeTime.description: The negotiated LifeTime of the IPSec Phase-1 IKE Tunnel in seconds.

hh3cIKETunActiveTime.name: hh3cIKETunActiveTime
hh3cIKETunActiveTime.description: The duration the IPSec Phase-1 IKE tunnel has been active in seconds.

hh3cIKETunRemainTime.name: hh3cIKETunRemainTime
hh3cIKETunRemainTime.description: The security association remaining time in seconds.

hh3cIKETunTotalRefreshes.name: hh3cIKETunTotalRefreshes
hh3cIKETunTotalRefreshes.description: The total number of security association refreshing performed.

hh3cIKETunDpdIntervalTime.name: hh3cIKETunDpdIntervalTime
hh3cIKETunDpdIntervalTime.description: The time that trigger DPD request. If ipsec message is expected to be sent out and the interval time between current time and the last time receiving peer's IPSec message is bigger than this time, DPD request would be triggered.

hh3cIKETunDpdTimeOut.name: hh3cIKETunDpdTimeOut
hh3cIKETunDpdTimeOut.description: The overtime of single DPD request. If DPD requests are refused three times, all security associations related would be deleted.

hh3cIKETunnelStatEntry.description: The entry contains the information of hh3cIKETunnelStatTable, such as the number of packets sent and received by the IKE tunnel, etc.
